## How We Work

Assessment and Target State  
We identify priority use cases, data readiness, risk constraints, and success metrics, then define a measurable target state.

Design and Architecture  
We design the operating model, including integrations, governance, security, lifecycle ownership, and performance requirements.

Build and Integrate  
We implement agents, automation, models, and analytics. These are integrated into real workflows and systems, not isolated experiments.

Validation and Deployment  
We test for reliability, safety, and performance, with evaluation practices appropriate for agentic systems and applied models.

Operate and Improve  
We establish monitoring, drift management, and improvement loops so AI performance strengthens over time.

